name: Art Doll Handmade Ooak Clay Character - Wendell
description: Wendell is a Ooak handmade clay character figure doll.  He is made entirely of clay and his totally hand sculpted.  Wendell is a very thoughtful little boy who generally likes to play for hours with his little red ball in his back yard.  His exterior is hand painted with acrylic paints and he stands about 10 inches tall.

name: Art Doll Handmade Ooak Clay Character - Blossom
description:
Blossom is a one of a kind totally handmade art doll. No molds or patterns were used in her creation. Her extremities are hand sculpted while her body is soft and contains an armature for posing. Blossom stands about 10 inches tall and would be a wonderful addition to your collectibles.

Her sweetness and innocence comes through in her expression and her body language. She is generally happy and excited about everything life has to offer.

name: Art Doll Ooak Handmade Clay Character - Danny Boy
description:
Art Doll Ooak Danny is a completely handmade clay creation. No molds or patterns were used in the sculpting. Danny is a doll that gets caught often in the "I Dunno" of life. Danny, it's tax time, are you ready? Danny, did you remember to this this? Danny did you ask them this? Did you take out the garbage? Why did you do that? Most times, the answer is "I Dunno".

The art doll stands about 10 inches tall - great shelf height. His head, hands and feet were hand sculpted and hard baked of polymer clay. His "gothic" saddened look, make it pretty clear that he is not having a very good day.
